  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Q*bert is a remake of the arcade game of the same name with three-dimensional (3D) graphics. It was developed by Artech Studios and released by Hasbro Interactive on the PlayStation and PC in 1999 and on the Dreamcast in 2000.\n\nQ*bert has 3 modes of play. Classic is like the original Q*bert, and the graphics can be changed from Retro to Modern. The Adventure mode takes Q*bert to 3D dimensions, and contains power ups and all new characters set in 4 worlds. Head to Head is a multiplayer mode.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
